Follow these steps to troubleshoot possible issues:
1. Make sure your device has entered the distribution network mode;
2. Make sure the WiFi password entered is correct;
3. Make sure the phone is connected to the wireless router 2.4GHz network;
4. Make sure that the wireless router has turned off the black list (mac address filtering) function;
5. Try to configure the wireless router to 11bg or 20Mhz bandwidth; after the distribution network is successful, reset the router to the original configuration.

